### **9. Account Resolution Pattern**

All channels follow this pattern:

```typescript
type ResolvedIrcAccount = {
  accountId: string;
  configured: boolean;
  enabled: boolean;
  host: string;
  port: number;
  tls: boolean;
  nick: string;
  name?: string;
  config: IrcAccountConfig;
  // ... more fields
